	<inceptionYear>2002</inceptionYear> <!-- yes, the first code was laid down in 2002! -->
	<description>
		ErmineJ performs analyses of gene sets in genomics studies. A typical goal is to determine whether
		particular biological pathways are "doing something interesting", given a ranked list of genes. The software is designed to be
		used by biologists with little or no informatics background.
	</description>
